      <title>金融科技公司 Pine Labs 考虑在印度进行 10 亿美元 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/fintech-firm-pine-labs-is-said-to-weigh-1-billion-ipo-in-india</link>
