      <title>法官称苹果公司不公平地解雇了一名参与有毒工作文化的英国员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/apple-unfairly-fired-a-uk-worker-who-was-part-toxic-work-culture-judge-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据英国法院的判决，苹果公司不公平地解雇了一名员工，原因是该员工发表了种族主义言论，而这种言论是其伦敦一家商店恶劣工作场所文化的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/apple-unfairly-fired-a-uk-worker-who-was-part-toxic-work-culture-judge-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:40:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
